    <h1>Dynamic settings injection</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">5.4=
</span>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-cur=
rent">2014.11</span></p>
<p><style type=3D"text/css">/*<![CDATA[*/
